        "other_refer": [],
        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The model coefficients and baseline survival to calculate 10-year risk of CVD are as follows:</span><b></b></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 246.382px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\"><colgroup><col width=\"112\" style=\"width: 30.8434%;\"><col width=\"151\" style=\"width: 32.2892%;\"><col width=\"91\" style=\"width: 19.2771%;\"><col width=\"94\" style=\"width: 17.5904%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk Factor</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Transformation</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Male</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Female</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Age, years</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>cage = (age &ndash; 60)/5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.3742</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.4648</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Smoking</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>current = 1, other = 0</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.6012</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.7744</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>SBP, mm Hg</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>csbp = (sbp &ndash; 120)/20</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.2777</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.3131</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Total cholesterol, mmol/L</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>ctchol = tchol &ndash; 6</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.1458</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.1002</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>HDL cholesterol, mmol/L</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>chdl = (hdl &ndash; 1.3)/0.5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.2698</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.2606</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Smoking*age interaction</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>smoking*cage</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.0755</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.1088</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>SBP*age interaction</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>csbp*cage</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.0255</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.0277</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Total cholesterol*age interaction</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>ctchol*cage</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.0281</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.0226</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>HDL cholesterol*age interaction</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>chdl*cage</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.0426</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.0613</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Baseline survival</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>0.9605</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>0.9776</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The uncalibrated 10-year risk of CVD is calculated by the following:</span><b></b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span><strong>10-year risk</strong> = 1 &ndash; (baseline survival)</span><sup><span>exp(x)</span></sup><span>,</span><b></b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>where <strong>x</strong> = &Sigma;[&beta;*(transformed variables)]</span><b></b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The region and sex-specific scales to calculate calibrated 10-year risk are as follows:</span></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"114\"><col width=\"85\"><col width=\"86\"><col width=\"84\"><col width=\"76\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Male</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Female</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk Region</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scale 1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scale 2</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scale 1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scale 2</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Low</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.5699</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.7476</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.7380</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.7019</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Moderate</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.1565</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.8009</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>-0.3143</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.7701</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>High</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.3207</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.9360</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.5710</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.9369</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Very high</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.5836</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.8294</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.9412</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0.8329</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The calibrated 10-year risk of CVD is calculated by the following:</span><span><b></b></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span><strong>Calibrated 10-year risk, %</strong> = [1 &ndash; exp(-exp(scale1 + scale2*ln(-ln(1 &ndash; 10-year risk))))]*100</span></p>",
        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Risk regions are defined by the following map:&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span><img src=\"https://s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/content/score2.png\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n<p>From <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34120177/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SCORE2 Working Group 2021</a>.</p>",
